WorldStage Newsonline– Vitafoam Plc has notified the Nigerian Stock Exchange and the investing public that an insider, Dr BO Makanjuola, a non executive director had purchased 53,404 more shares at N5.87k which amounted to N313,481.48 The notified signed by Olalekan Sanni, Company Secretary said the transaction took place on 23rd, 24th, 25th September 2020. WorldStage earlier reported recent purchase of 78,320 shares at N5.55k  per share by Makanjuola.